once upon a time there was a monkey who reside on jamun tree, which was on the banks of the river, in the forest
one day crocodile came to the banks of the river and rested under the tree.The kind hearted monkey offered him fruits.
the crocodile came the next day for more fruits.As days passed the crocodile and monkey became friends.The crocodile tried to eat the monkey so he devised a plan.
He tried to force the monkey to come down and go with hom in the middle of the river so that he can eat it.The monkey was very clever and did not come in the idea of the crocodile.
The crocodile forced the monkey to coe.As he came in the middle of the river the crocodile said that he wanted the monkey to be eaten by his wife.